Hey everyone, the best solution I've come up with for this as of Feb 2025 is to unfocus from the text field before accessing ImagePicker, then refocusing once the image is selected.

Example

```dart
GestureDetector(
  onTap: () async {
   // Close the keyboard
    FocusManager.instance.primaryFocus?.unfocus();

   // Access the image
    final media =
        await ImagePicker().pickImage(source: ImageSource.gallery);

    if (media != null && context.mounted) {
      context.read<CommunityChatBloc>().add(
            CCEAddImageRequested(media),
          );

      // Re-focus the textfield you are using
      context.read<CommunityChatBloc>().focusNode.requestFocus();
    }
  },
  child: theme.icons.photoVideoIcon(
    width: 20,
    height: 20,
  ),
),
```

